Welcome to GreenSTOP ™

GreenSTOP LLC is a “hands off” (ancillary) technology company creating software and hardware applications for the legal cannabis market. Our technology will help expedite, brand, and professionalize the cannabis buying experience in current legal dispensaries.

Pre-Register for our mobile app for a chance to win amazing prizes! (Learn more)

World's first ever cannabis smart dispensary

  • Automated Kiosk (Smart Dispensary)
  • Delivery (Multiple Platforms)
  • Mobile App (Coming Soon)

Smart Dispensary

"The Smart Dispensary!" GreenSTOP offers a two prong solution to problems in today's legal cannabis industry. GreenSTOP utilizes an in store Automated Cannabis Dispensary (ACD) system and revolutionary mobile app that work together to make purchasing cannabis more reliable and convenient than ever before! The in store pick up and home delivery experience for consumers will never be the same.

ACD

The GreenSTOP ACD Automated Cannabis Dispensary is the first of its kind and its functionality has never before been seen in any industry. (Learn more)
  • 3D Viewing
  • Pre-Order/Pick-Up
  • Video Chat with Agent
*World's Most Innovative Kiosk Premieres on Venture Cannabis ™ this Season

Mobile App

The GreenSTOP mobile app will bring the most convenient cannabis delivery platform ever introduced to the cannabis industry.(Learn more)
  • Pre-Screen/Pre-Order
  • Instant Pick-Up at Kiosk
  • 30 min Delivery Guarantee

Venture Cannabis ™

Reality Television Series | Length: 1 Hour

Venture Cannabis follows two Serial Entrepreneurs (James and Timothy) as they chase their dream of creating the first billion-dollar tech comppany in Cannabis (GreenSTOP).

Creator: James Edwards & Timothy Island.
Directed by: Darien F. Rodriguez

Mission Statement

GreenSTOP is a two prong solution to major problems in the growing legal cannabis industry. The GreenSTOP umbrella will bring branding and technology to an industry that is growing fast but is in desperate need of some corner stone companies.
